properties.description:
*** There are multiple warnings for this area. To see all current warnings, visit the QFES Current Bushfires and Warnings website ***

A fire is burning in the vicinity of Powerhouse Road, Cloncurry. It is moving towards Powerhouse Road. ‎

‎
properties.title: incident: fire vegetation

properties.description: Smoke is currently affecting areas between Mount Isa and Cloncurry. This is from multiple fires burning in the area, including Powerhouse Road and Roxmere Road, Cloncurry and parts of the Barkly Highway.
properties.title: incident: fire vegetation

properties.description: There is a vegetation fire at this location. Smoke may affect residents and motorists in the area. Residents should close their doors and windows and keep medication close by if suffering from a respiratory condition. Motorists should use caution and drive to conditions. If you believe your property is under threat, you should call Triple Zero (000) immediately.
